data.description: PRICE REDUCTION submit offers for Seller(s) to review!!!!  Tri-Plex located in a beautiful residential and mix multi units housings.  Located East Euclid Ave and North of Arrow Hwy and between the 210 fwy to the North and 10 fwy to the South and in treelined streets for strolling and fitness runs.  Located near Downtown Upland, City Hall, Library, Schools public and private, Post Office, mix of familiar and boutique restaurants and Metro-link and public transportation.  The units provide a harmonious balance between functionality and appeal, ensuring a comfortable living experience.  Each unit has 2 spacious bedrooms and 1 full bath, living area, dining area, kitchen, laundry, 4 detached garages rear of property and open side yard. Unit 576 has had no recent upgrades or changes in the last year.  Unit 578 and 580 have had recent repairs and upgrades in the last 6 months to the interior. Wall heaters in each unit, ceiling fans and window cooling units.  Each unit has separate Gas and Electric meters.  Owner pays water and trash.  Existing tenants are on a month to month basis and have been long term.  There is off-street parking on 11th street and 4 enclosed garages in the back **note 2 garages were converted to an office/den/storage/closet with entry from unit 3/#580 buyer choice to convert back to garages, non permitted.  Don't miss this chance to make a GREAT INVESTMENT!!!
